Package Admins

Class Admin

java.lang.Object
Users.Users
Users.Staff
Admins.Admin
public class Admin extends Staff
The Admin class represents an administrator in the system. This class extends the Staff class, inheriting common attributes for all staff members. It can be used to store and manage information specific to admin users.

There are two constructors available:

  • A default constructor that initializes an empty Admin object.
  • A parameterized constructor that initializes an Admin with specified attributes.
